data.title: Strategy slips as bitcoin selloff prompts sharp forecast cut
data.description: ** Shares of bitcoin buyer Strategy NASDAQ:MSTR drop 4.6% to $169.33 premarket** Co slashes 2025 earnings forecast after massive drop in bitcoin prices** MSTR's updated 2025 outlook ranges from a loss of $17 per share to a profit of $19 per share, compared with its previous forecast of $80 per shar…
